{% extends "layout.njk" %}
{% from "form.njk" import csrfProtection, submitButton, errorSummary %}

{% set heading = 'Using an expert in small claims' %}
{% block content %}
<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    <p>{{ t('It’s rare for judges to allow you to use an expert in a small claim.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('You must ask for permission to use an expert - a judge will then decide whether the expert is necessary.') }}
    <p>{{ t('The judge will also decide whether the cost of the expert is reasonable compared to the value of the claim.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('Even though you and the {{ otherParty }} share the cost of hiring the expert, judges are still responsible for keeping costs in proportion to value.',
        { otherParty: otherParty }) }}</p>

    <h2 class="heading-medium">{{ t('When an expert is allowed') }}</h2>
    <p>{{ t('A judge will only allow you to use an expert if they believe they need the expert’s specialist knowledge.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('For example, they might allow a structural engineer to be used in a claim about building works or a mechanic in a claim about car repairs.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('If a judge allows you to use an expert, you’ll usually have to share one expert with the {{ otherParty }}.', { otherParty: otherParty }) }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('The expert will provide a written report - they won’t usually come to court in person.') }}</p>

    <h2 class="heading-medium">{{ t('Paying for the expert') }}</h2>
    <p>{{ t('The cost of hiring an expert depends on which expert you and the {{ otherParty }} choose.', { otherParty: otherParty }) }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('Usually you both share this cost.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('If you win the case you may be able to recover a maximum of £750 of the cost you paid. A judge will rule on this at the end of the hearing.') }}</p>

    <h2 class="heading-medium">{{ t('If you get permission to use an expert') }}</h2>
    <p>{{ t('The judge may ask one of you to make a list of 3 independent experts who can provide a written report in return for a fee.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('You must avoid discussing the case in detail with the 3 experts.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ t('The other party then chooses one expert from the list. After that, you both need to follow these steps:') }}</p>
    <ul class="list list-number">
      <li>{{ t('Provide questions for the expert to answer in a report.') }}</li>
      <li>{{ t('Provide any extra information the expert asks for.') }}</li>
      <li>{{ t('Pay the expert - you usually both share this cost.') }}</li>
    </ul>
    <form method="post">
      {{ csrfProtection(csrf) }}
      {{ submitButton() }}
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
